    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build your own islands as a gigantic tentacled beast in this creative sandbox demo.</strong> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276400/extras/6b3b44b183d54aeaa38418bfa41bb82d.poster.avif?t=1734618975\" width=704 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276400/extras/6b3b44b183d54aeaa38418bfa41bb82d.webm?t=1734618975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276400/extras/6b3b44b183d54aeaa38418bfa41bb82d.mp4?t=1734618975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using the mighty Creation Glove, build structures, clone objects, paint buildings, and lay down roads, then use the human waypoint tool to populate your creations. Share your creations via Steam Workshop or visit islands from other players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276400/extras/9283550b93a3b11a6878efa313837d68.poster.avif?t=1734618975\" width=704 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276400/extras/9283550b93a3b11a6878efa313837d68.webm?t=1734618975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276400/extras/9283550b93a3b11a6878efa313837d68.mp4?t=1734618975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> You can choose to be benevolent rulers, or wreck havoc on your newly formed civilizations – it’s your choice!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276400/extras/98134a631948fd96d99ff6595d7bef22.poster.avif?t=1734618975\" width=702 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276400/extras/98134a631948fd96d99ff6595d7bef22.webm?t=1734618975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276400/extras/98134a631948fd96d99ff6595d7bef22.mp4?t=1734618975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick from a huge selection of more than 400 objects to create and populate your little (or big) islands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276400/extras/c0a3294f3e040a02446a6d0c80117150.avif?t=1734618975\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276400/extras_big/c0a3294f3e040a02446a6d0c80117150.avif?t=1734618975 width=800 height=282 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tentacular Playgrounds let`s you experience the sandbox part of Tentacular. <i></i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
